      Chasing Dead is a story-based,  Sci-fi/Horror  First-Person  Action
      Shooter. The game begins with a strange phenomenon in which another
      Earth  appears  in  our  skies.  The  curiosity  and  fear    of  a
      doppelganger planet initiates multiple missions in  order  to  make
      contact with the duplicate Earth. A team of agents, astronauts, and
      scientists were sent 955,600 miles across space by NASA and  the US
      Military, however  all contact  is lost  a few  hours  after  their
      arrival.
